MCI COMMUNICATION SERVICES, INC., Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
DIRECTOR, DIVISION OF TAXATION, Defendant-Respondent. C-170 September Term 2018
081488 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 18, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005735-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
